<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3689">‌أَبُو سَعِيدٍ الْأَشَجُّ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2588">‌أَبُو خَالِدٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> أَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">‌حُمَيْدٌ </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣١٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُ: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ أَمَرَ بِالِاقْتِصَاصِ مِنَ السِّنِّ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> كِتَابُ اللهِ الْقِصَاصُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>